duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide administrative and operational support for the whole real estate team
Responsible for tasks ranging from transaction management to event planning and running errands
Exceed customer expectations by providing assistance with a positive attitude and timely follow-up on customer requests and commitments
Create a welcoming environment through teamwork and collaboration
Effectively utilize technology to communicate with the team and clients, and utilize available clientele tools to increase business
Develop long term customer relationships and demonstrate flexibility to adapt to the changing needs of the business
